Summary of changes for openmpi_ext 1.1.1:
-------------------------------------------------------------------

 * The openmpi_ext package has been renamed to "mpi". To avoid transition problems, this
    new release is merely a dummy package with no functions, and dependent
    on the new version of the mpi package.


Summary of changes for openmpi_ext 1.1.0:
-------------------------------------------------------------------

 * Added help text and demos in all example scripts

 * Code clean-up and standardization, and some bug-fixes

